### Get all events
GET {{host}}/api/events/

### Get event by ID
GET {{host}}/api/events/1

### Create a new event
POST {{host}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Summer Music Festival",
  "description": "A weekend of great music and fun",
  "date": "2024-10-15T18:00:00",
  "location": "Central Park",
  "capacity": 5000,
  "price": 49.99
}

### Update an event
PUT {{host}}/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Summer Music Festival",
  "description": "An updated weekend of great music and fun",
  "date": "2024-07-16T18:00:00",
  "location": "Central Park",
  "capacity": 6000,
  "price": 59.99,
  "category": "MUSIC"
}

### Delete an event
DELETE {{host}}/api/events/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get events by organizer
GET {{host}}/api/events/organizer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
